# PostHog web analytics — see docs/plans/2026-05-28-001-feat-posthog-web-analytics-plan.md
# Set both vars in Cloudflare Pages → Settings → Environment variables (Production scope)
# so they're available at build time (Astro inlines PUBLIC_* into the generated HTML).
# Leave unset locally to skip the snippet and avoid polluting prod analytics during dev.
PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=
PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST=https://eu.i.posthog.com
